<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你就那样跑掉，太没礼貌了。”她责备道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很难过。”拇指姑娘说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她忘不了皮特躺在地道的场景。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就因为那只蠢鸟吗？”格雷夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一整天都没和拇指姑娘说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上她很早就上床睡觉了，让拇指姑娘自己一个人呆着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的皮特。”拇指姑娘边哭边说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能让他自己孤零零地躺在那里，好像没人关心他一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘抓起了一条格雷夫人的毯子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皮特是我的朋友，应该用什么盖住他的身体。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是她提起灯，悄悄地打开后门，走进了通向皮特的地道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当拇指姑娘看到皮特躺在那里的时候，心又痛了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还记得你把这条绳子给我的那个时候。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她把绳子从皮特的腿上解了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘用毯子盖住皮特的尸体，在他旁边坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬头看着洞外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“星星真美啊，皮特。”她小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你再也见不到它们了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘开始哭泣，她把头埋在皮特的胸膛里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听见皮特羽毛里传来一个微弱的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰。拇指姑娘努力地听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰。声音越来越大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰。皮特的心脏还在跳动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他还活着！皮特！”拇指姑娘几乎大声喊了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在哪里？”皮特一边说，一边缓缓的睁开眼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是你吗？拇指姑娘？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不敢相信这是真的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皮特！你还活着！我真是太开心了。”她一边喊一边抱住了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我感觉暖和多了。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来帮你。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她飞快的跑向格雷夫人的家，取了一些水之后马上跑了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么在这儿，拇指姑娘？”皮特喝了一些水之后，问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘大声叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在跟一只很亲切的老鼠住在一起，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是她想让我嫁给洛夫斯先生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁是洛夫斯先生？”皮特问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是一只鼹鼠。”拇指姑娘回答说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他住在地底下，他还很讨厌阳光！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她没把洛夫斯先生也讨厌鸟的事情告诉皮特。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那太糟糕了！”皮特说，“我们得想想办法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是首先你得好起来。”拇指姑娘说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，拇指姑娘把婚纱铺在地板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把格雷夫人橱柜里的坚果和种子放在婚纱上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把婚纱的角绑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把婚纱拽到皮特身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃了这些食物之后你会感觉好点的。”拇指姑娘说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了几天，皮特恢复了一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想知道你发生了什么事。”拇指姑娘说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特点点头：“嗯，让我慢慢地告诉你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>